      <br /> 输出：
      <br /> 
      <ul>
       <li><font face="微软雅黑, &amp;quot;">支持2、3、4、5张混合贴图，只占用1 DrawCall</font></li>
       <li><font face="微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei">材质预览：<br /> diffuse<br /> <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=16521&amp;aid=6105&amp;from=album&amp;page=1&amp;mobile=2" class="orange"><img id="aimg_6105" src="forum.php?mod=image&amp;aid=6105&amp;size=140x140&amp;key=a56f2398d3a255c1&amp;type=fixnone" alt="SinglePassMaterial.jpg" title="SinglePassMaterial.jpg" /></a> <br /> bumped diffuse<br /> <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=16521&amp;aid=6106&amp;from=album&amp;page=1&amp;mobile=2" class="orange"><img id="aimg_6106" src="forum.php?mod=image&amp;aid=6106&amp;size=140x140&amp;key=0a39ecece2aba7a8&amp;type=fixnone" alt="SinglePassMaterial_another.jpg" title="SinglePassMaterial_another.jpg" /></a> <br /> </font></li>
